OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fcontinue to affect the northeast of
OL,7,FScotland overnight, with increasing
OL,8,Fcloud also generating a few showers
OL,9,Fnear to the east coast of England
OL,10,Flater. Becoming mostly dry elsewhere
OL,11,Fwith clear periods. Some fog and frost
OL,12,Fforming.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FEarly showers in the north and
OL,15,Feast, breaking out more widely during
OL,16,Fthe day, and turning locally heavy.
OL,17,FSome southern and western areas
OL,18,Fstaying mostly fine, with some warm
OL,19,Fsunshine.
